title: Chicago Shipwreck - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/12/22
itunes:title: Chicago Shipwreck - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/12/22
description:
Guest host Richard Syrett and author Natalie Zett discuss a little known boating accident in Chicago in 1915 that claimed the lives of more than 800 people, and how the spirit of her great aunt who died in the tragedy communicated with her to tell the story.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
